#: ../../source/manpages/libunbound.rst:264
msgid ""
"Set machine to forward DNS queries to, the caching resolver to use. IP4 "
"or IP6 address. Forwards all DNS requests to that machine, which is "
"expected to run a recursive resolver. If the proxy is not DNSSEC capable,"
" validation may fail. Can be called several times, in that case the "
"addresses are used as backup servers. At this time it is only possible to"
" set configuration before the first resolve is done."
msgstr ""

