"IP4 or IP6 address. If the address is NULL the stub entry is removed. Set"
" isprime true if you configure root hints with it. Otherwise similar to "
"the stub zone item from unbound's config file. Can be called several "
"times, for different zones, or to add multiple addresses for a particular"
" zone. At this time it is only possible to set configuration before the "
"first resolve is done."
msgstr ""

