#: ../../source/manpages/unbound.conf.rst:3770
msgid ""
"With :ref:`allow-notify:<unbound.conf.auth.allow-notify>` you can specify"
" additional sources of notifies. When notified, the server attempts to "
"first probe and then zone transfer. If the notify is from a primary, it "
